ParseX-Yapp version 0.0.1

Extensions to Parse::Yapp to handle some common patterns. Basically to make
things look a little more like Parse::RecDescent.

It'll remain pure perl, and I don't envision any system dependencies.

INSTALLATION

To install this module, run the following commands:

	perl Makefile.PL
	make
	make test
	make install

Alternatively, to install with Module::Build, you can use the following commands:

	perl Build.PL
	./Build
	./Build test
	./Build install


DEPENDENCIES

None.


